node.text: Omg this kimono is so fab!!!

When you have been away from people for 108 days and you start to think this must be normal morning coffee attire 👘 . .
.
.
Hi neighbors. 👋🏻 Nothing to see here. Question: At what ages do you go from weird to different to unique to crazy to eccentric? Feel like you can only be eccentric as a retiree. I’d like to adopt that title now. Change approved. .
.
.
Vintage kimono from @etsy 
Sunglasses @aldo_shoes
I always wear a fabulous kimono when I drink my coffee! 😉
@templecandles oh yes. And maybe will take up an accent.
Planning on going ‘full eccentric’ mode in retirement! 🤣
@maishaconcept regal and ridiculous. Weighs a ton!
@instantgoddess we did adopt a pet lizard this morning. We had caught her and put her outside and now she’s back. We know it’s the same one because her tail fell off in the chase. 😅
Loving your morning get-up! I need to up my game crazy lady 😆 you don’t have any cats though. This is disappointing. You need to try harder! 😜
Wearing nice flowy dresses at home super helps feel like you're on a chill vacation not in prison🤷🏼‍♀️
Love the glam coffee in the morning.
Omg this kimono is so fab!!!
